name: Starrelic - Stararmor
desc: When a monster is Flip Summoned: You can Special Summon this card from your hand. If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can add 1 "Starrelic" card from your Deck to your hand. If you control this Normal Summoned/Set monster (Quick Effect): You can target 1 face-up monster your opponent controls that was Special Summoned from the Extra Deck; return both it and this card to the hand. You can only use each effect of "Starrelic - Stararmor" once per turn.
